caption: Fiscal Management
created: 20260405120000000
modified: 20260405120000000
title: Policy2100(C)
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

* Prepare and recommend an annual budget that reflects district priorities and fiscal responsibility.
* Oversee the administration of district finances, grants, and resources in compliance with state and federal laws.
* Keep the Board informed regarding the financial status of the district.
